    <title>阿里灵杰_Task01_环境配置、实践数据下载</title>
    <url>/330NJ94/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="0x00-Abstract"><a href="#0x00-Abstract" class="headerlink" title="0x00 Abstract"></a>0x00 Abstract</h2><ul>
<li>任务内容：<ul>
<li>从比赛官网下载数据集，并使用 Python 读取数据</li>
<li>使用 <code>jieba</code> 对文本进行分词</li>
<li>使用 <code>TFIDF</code> 对文本进行编码</li>
<li>思考如何使用 TFIDF 计算文本相似度？</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>学习资料： <a href="https://coggle.club/blog/tianchi-open-search">https://coggle.club/blog/tianchi-open-search</a><span id="more"></span></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="0x01-读取数据"><a href="#0x01-读取数据" class="headerlink" title="0x01 读取数据"></a>0x01 读取数据</h2><p>这里只用 <code>train.query.txt</code> 中的前十条数据。同整个数据集的数据处理同理。</p>
<p>首先导入需要用到的包：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="keyword">as</span> pd</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> jieba</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> gensim <span class="keyword">import</span> corpora, models, similarities</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>读取数据：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;data/train.query.txt&#x27;</span>, encoding=<span class="string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">    train_querys = f.readlines()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">train_query = &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> line <span class="keyword">in</span> train_querys:</span><br><span class="line">    line = line.strip().split(<span class="string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    query_id = line[<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line">    query = line[<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line">    train_query[<span class="built_in">int</span>(query_id)] = query</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>取字典 <code>train_query</code> 的前十条数据：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 字典切片</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">dict_slice</span>(<span class="params">adict, start, end</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    keys = adict.keys()</span><br><span class="line">    dict_slice = &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> k <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">list</span>(keys)[start:end]:</span><br><span class="line">        dict_slice[k] = adict[k]</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> dict_slice</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">wordListTop10 = dict_slice (train_query, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line">wordListTop10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>{1: ‘美赞臣亲舒一段’,<br>2: ‘慱朗手动料理机’,<br>3: ‘電力貓’,<br>4: ‘掏夹缝工具’,<br>5: ‘飞推 vip’,<br>6: ‘多功能托地把’,<br>7: ‘充气浮力袖’,<br>8: ‘盒马花胶鸡汤锅’,<br>9: ‘塞塞乐’,<br>10: ‘广汽传祺 gs5 挡风遮雨条子’}</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="0x02-使用-jieba-对文本进行分词"><a href="#0x02-使用-jieba-对文本进行分词" class="headerlink" title="0x02 使用 jieba 对文本进行分词"></a>0x02 使用 <code>jieba</code> 对文本进行分词</h2><p>使用 <code>jieba</code> 中的搜索引擎模式对文本分词。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>搜索引擎模式：将结果精确分开，对比较长的词进行二次切分。</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">seg_list = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">11</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    seg = jieba.cut_for_search(wordListTop10[i])</span><br><span class="line">    seg_list.append (seg) <span class="comment"># 把前10个数据的所有分词放进一个列表中</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="0x03-使用-TFIDF-对文本进行编码"><a href="#0x03-使用-TFIDF-对文本进行编码" class="headerlink" title="0x03 使用 TFIDF 对文本进行编码"></a>0x03 使用 <code>TFIDF</code> 对文本进行编码</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 制作字典</span></span><br><span class="line">dictionary = corpora.Dictionary(seg_list)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 可以通过token2id得到特征数字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(dictionary.token2id)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>{‘一段’: 0, ‘亲舒’: 1, ‘美赞臣’: 2, ‘赞臣’: 3, ‘慱’: 4, ‘手动’: 5, ‘料理’: 6, ‘朗’: 7, ‘机’: 8, ‘電力貓’: 9, ‘夹缝’: 10, ‘工具’: 11, ‘掏’: 12, ‘vip’: 13, ‘推’: 14, ‘飞’: 15, ‘功能’: 16, ‘多功能’: 17, ‘托地’: 18, ‘把’: 19, ‘充气’: 20, ‘浮力’: 21, ‘袖’: 22, ‘盒马花胶’: 23, ‘锅’: 24, ‘鸡汤’: 25, ‘乐’: 26, ‘塞塞’: 27, ‘gs5’: 28, ‘广汽传祺’: 29, ‘挡风’: 30, ‘挡风遮雨’: 31, ‘条子’: 32, ‘遮雨’: 33}</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 制作数字向量类型的语料库（doc2bow）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ----&gt; 将字符串转换成数字向量类型的词袋模型(稀疏向量)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 源文件不做处理是一个字符串类型的语料库</span></span><br><span class="line">corpus = [dictionary.doc2bow (doc) <span class="keyword">for</span> doc <span class="keyword">in</span> seg_list]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Conclusion"><a href="#Conclusion" class="headerlink" title="Conclusion"></a>Conclusion</h2><p>没有做过 NLP 的东西，趁着做今天的任务，大概了解了分词，文本向量化表示（词袋模型）之类的内容。</p>
]]></content>
